---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import { SITE_CONFIG } from '~/lib/siteConfig'

const updated = '2026-06-19'
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`Grievance officer — ${SITE_CONFIG.name}`}
  description="Mandatory contact under India's IT Rules 2021."
>
  <header class="container-prose page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow"><a href="/">{SITE_CONFIG.name}</a> / <a href="/legal/">Legal</a> / Grievance officer</p>
    <h1>Grievance officer</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
  </header>

  <article class="container-prose prose">
    <p>
      Per the <strong>Information Technology (Intermediary Guidelines and Digital
      Media Ethics Code) Rules, 2021</strong>, the following contact handles
      complaints related to {SITE_CONFIG.origin} and the rest of the oriz family.
    </p>

    <div class="card">
      <p><strong>Name:</strong> Chirag Singhal</p>
      <p><strong>Designation:</strong> Grievance Officer</p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:whyiswhen@gmail.com">whyiswhen@gmail.com</a></p>
      <p><strong>Address:</strong> Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India 751001</p>
      <p><strong>Response time:</strong> Acknowledgement within 24 hours; resolution within 15 days.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>What you can report</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Content on {SITE_CONFIG.name} that infringes your copyright (DMCA / Indian copyright complaints).</li>
      <li>Content that violates the IT Rules (defamation, obscenity, threats, impersonation).</li>
      <li>Privacy concerns under the DPDP Act 2023 — access, correction, deletion of your data.</li>
      <li>Account takeover or security incidents.</li>
      <li>Calculator-correctness disputes — a formula or assumption you believe is wrong.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Please include: a clear description of the issue, the URL(s) involved,
      proof you are the rights-holder (for copyright), and your contact details.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-head { padding-block: 3rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .eyebrow { color: var(--color-fg-muted); font-size: 0.8125rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
  .eyebrow a { color: var(--color-fg-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0; }
  .meta { color: var(--color-fg-soft); font-size: 0.875rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0; }
  .prose { padding-block: 2.5rem 4rem; color: var(--color-prose); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.0625rem; }
  .prose h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.375rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 2rem 0 1rem; }
  .prose ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
  .prose li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
  .prose a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .card {
    margin-block: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
  }
  .card p { margin: 0.375rem 0; }
</style>
